latestIgtvVideos.title: My night-time skincare regime ft. @forestessentials
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Knowing what you are feeding your skin is as important as knowing what you are feeding your body. For that very reason, I've been trying to gradually shift to using all natural products from brands that practice complete transparency with their ingredients. One of my favourites in the category - Forest Essentials has some amazing products that always suit my overly sensitive skin so I thought I'll share the ones I've been using for my nighttime regime with you guys :) Listing down the products shown stepwise in the video:

Step 1 // Multani Mitti ubtan for deep cleansing and exfoliating. This rich alkaline soil containing minerals and volcanic ash corrects imbalances and neutralizes skin tone. It can be used as a cleanser, exfoliator, as a de-tan and for removing pigmentation, as an anti acne face masque and so much more! 
Step 2 // Bela Facial Tonic Mist. This pure and active water-based toner contains steam distilled water of Bela flowers that hydrates, tones and revives the skin along with minimising enlarged pores. You can refrigerate in summers and use it after cleansing, or as often as required during the day to keep the skin fresh and hydrated.

Step 3 // Ojas Glow replenishing Night Beauty Balm. It is formulated with 40% of a unique repairing and brightening Ayurvedic serum that has intricate rituals of making. The fragrance of the beauty balm is naturally herbal without any added fragrance and it leaves the skin looking visibly energized with a youthful appearance.

Step 4 // Night Treatment Cream Jasmine & Patchouli. Specially created for combination to oily skin, this nourishing cream is a natural source of antioxidants, slows down and prevents signs of ageing, neutralizes oil production and gives the skin an even tone.

Also guys, I love that it was super easy to restock my essentials by ordering from their website and feels great to know that the brand is taking care to ensure the products reach you sanitized at every step of the way! 
#FEForMe #RitualsByFE #LuxuryOfPurity #LuxuriousAyurveda #ForestEssentials
